UID:10003126-1782554400-1782567000@lancastersciencefactory.org
SUMMARY:Reptile Discovery Day
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun filled day with Forgotten Friend Reptile Sanctuary. There will be 3 shows\, each followed with a time for questions and a chance to touch the reptiles. At this time\, we do not know which animals they will be bringing to the Science Factory\, but we know it will be an exciting chance to learn more about them. \nShow times: 10:30am\, 11:30am\, and 12:30pm. \nThis event is free with admission. Your ticket to The Lancaster Science Factory does NOT guarantee you admission to the shows. \n 
URL:https://lancastersciencefactory.org/event/reptile-discovery-day/
LOCATION:The Lancaster Science Factory\, 454 New Holland Ave\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancastersciencefactory.org/wp-content/uploads/Reptile-Discovery-Day-Event-Banner.png
GEO:40.0461822;-76.2963319
