SUMMARY:Brain Freeze: The Science of Ice Cream
DESCRIPTION:Brain Freeze: The Science of Ice Cream is presented by Lancaster Country Day School. This event is free with admission \nStop by the Lancaster Science Factory on Sunday\, July 19 from 10-3 to learn how ice cream is made and what makes it so good! \nMore details to come!
